{"tid":176440,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"title對轉工有幾大幫助？","createTime":"2017-03-28T07:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T11:34:00.000Z","uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47159b4aa858b57f8e667552f5999af424af8708","tid":176440,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"我係公司底層員工，internal title都係聽落都係雜兵之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但而加公司因為某d原因high pay（以同grade計）請我，大約30近40k<br />\n<br />\n最近有公司俾offer我，人工加左1x%，title係manager，等於我而加公司跳左幾級，如果新公司知我而加internal grade會唔會壓我價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n借人ac用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4ccff0a32ac2137e1be953a66ce1d3ff405351","tid":176440,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"新公司點會知<br />\n<br />\n佢請你係要能力唔會係要title"},{"pid":"14913678ec6584bd3fa78657c790b8ca620ef074","tid":176440,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"轉工睇人工姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c116f7bef0ad37501d3337a94d9afe480920f386","tid":176440,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"我都想問<br />\n宜家做BANK 既OPERATION OFFICER 算唔算TITLE 見得下人?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eaf52b46af3ff76af8a3e48fa7661c6bed8c0e7","tid":176440,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想問<br />\n宜家做BANK 既OPERATION OFFICER 算唔算TITLE 見得下人?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同我一樣聽上去就係雜兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實銀行am都ok 低級，但睇部門"},{"pid":"c251c89c4c81eabf89fff106c2b09a87aaf44398","tid":176440,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"你過自己 底層? 但又加到差不多40K 巴打你好勁喎(雖然唔知你個原因係咩)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297a01a99e482a432421300ca2b0e9b745f62b85","tid":176440,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想問<br />\n宜家做BANK 既OPERATION OFFICER 算唔算TITLE 見得下人?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間間公司既普通staff都係叫officer<br />\n大d咪有2萬蚊到"},{"pid":"fdea99d5cce787dd8625389633049033ee72988e","tid":176440,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"中銀back office大約咁分:<br />\nClerk -&gt; Senior Clerk -&gt; Officer -&gt; Senior Officer -&gt; Deputy Manager -&gt; Manager -&gt; Senior Manager<br />\n大約咁上下啦 (但全中文)<br />\n另外會出現同職位但不同職等<br />\n如Clerk 可以係職等3或職等4"},{"pid":"ece428667111f3133aa5bdf64a9145592cf3b818","tid":176440,"uid":67867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"40k既雜兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你本身報時CV冇title架咩"},{"pid":"e16df1436c45d83f26cf216b51c36acad7c2e36b","tid":176440,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:22:21.000Z","msg":"有料咪得"},{"pid":"90b7deabee0345c355cd0fb27d2174c91193d175","tid":176440,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>40k既雜兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你本身報時CV冇title架咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算專業人士出身，但做既時間唔長，不過有其他經歷令我加左唔少人工<br />\n<br />\n而加間公司想請我專業相關既人，但無人肯入呢間公司到做，佢嫌我年資少，唔肯俾高d grade我，出offer俾我果陣仲想我唔加人工甚至discount，我企硬要加兩成。最後係佢地急要人同請唔到人既情況下谷俾high pay我<br />\n<br />\n我得internal grade但無正式title，間公司話會俾個external title我，但做左大半年都無俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  cv個title我自己寫落去，寫得含糊d，可圈可點，但internal grade個名真係唔太好聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過而加間公司成個制度都係on99，早走早着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e51422f2068cfc2a543928aeb93c88b2b4e6922","tid":176440,"uid":55125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"人工代表所有"},{"pid":"a2ee9e0f5bb27b2d6bbcadcb5bd266f8cf954ebd","tid":176440,"uid":17808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"邊行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75d4b7c51b4ecbb6d2efd5e3f06a90418857ebe","tid":176440,"uid":15859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"收左offer<br />\n仲有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你自己作external title 去mislead人可以比人告<br />\n但你舊公司如果認可你用個external 去自稱都可以兜既"},{"pid":"104729d295ec9badde187a9948061682f8024566","tid":176440,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收左offer<br />\n仲有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你自己作external title 去mislead人可以比人告<br />\n但你舊公司如果認可你用個external 去自稱都可以兜既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經叫寫得合理，我同事仲低我一grade，公司幫佢出既卡片寫得好似仲高級過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290fef29bb7fed11a478b0c91a63fbb9057fd42b","tid":176440,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:34:00.000Z","msg":"好似倒轉左咁<br />\n有左offer 呢d 仲需要諗架咩?<br />\n<br />\n唔係見工前已經知你個title ka 咩?"}]}